    # s "Didn't my father tell you what the danger was, though?"
    s ""

translate ru ArrivingInLethram_9fdaf526:
    # "Kate corrected some of Sarah's hair."
    ""

translate ru ArrivingInLethram_9581947a:
    # k "Sarah...just have faith...ok? It will all work out."
    k ""

translate ru ArrivingInLethram_b2660f71:
    # "Kate suddenly got up, grabbing both of their bags."
    ""

translate ru ArrivingInLethram_0f48e9f1:
    # k "I need to get some things sorted. You stay here, in the tent, where you're safe. I'll be back soon when I know more, ok?"
    k ""

translate ru ArrivingInLethram_178795cb:
    # "Sarah nodded, and her friend left the tent."
    ""

translate ru ArrivingInLethram_25e4bb05:
    # "Despite being surrounded by the bustle of the mercenary camp, Sarah suddenly felt very alone."
    ""

translate ru ArrivingInLethram_64300172:
    # "It had been the first time since she and Kate had gone on the run, that she had actually been alone."
    ""

translate ru ArrivingInLethram_0abf849b:
    # "Sarah pulled up her legs, resting her chin on her knees."
    ""

translate ru ArrivingInLethram_1bad6a23:
    # "What did I do...she wondered to herself."
    ""

